                    When everyone follows the framework's best practices, this is what happens:
                </p>

                <ul class="mt-4">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                        <x-heroicon-o-check-circle class="flex-shrink-0 text-indigo-400 translate-y-[3.5px] w-4 h-4" />
